{"tid":1745303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果再有屍體發現案，現場手足可唔可以行多一步？","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:15:28.000Z","uid":70786,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"746b9180ed03b9489ee0d8d16a8b238d97f9157b","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"之前就話一定影大頭等手足唔會死得不明不白<br />\n依家懷疑花式吸氦氣自殺等你地影唔到<br />\n其實發現屍體嘅人可唔可以勇敢少少？<br />\n未有警察嚟之前，揭開個膠袋睇下佢仲有冇呼吸<br />\n盡公民責任去拯救一個垂死嘅人<br />\n順便睇下頭部有冇明顯傷痕<br />\n唔好同我講驚，手足死之前好可能比你驚一千倍一萬倍<br />\n為手足少少心理關口都跨唔過？<br />\n<br />\n有警察嚟咗，就扮識個死者，歇斯底里喊晒口咁要見佢最後一面<br />\n見男就嗌細佬，見女就叫阿妹<br />\n話自己個細佬／妹出街都係著呢套衫，總之就係死要見屍<br />\n<br />\n如果唔方便影相，就等其他在場人士影，最緊要係除咗個頭套"},{"pid":"bd567cacc75ef2a11d5ce0a70ffecb4e346fef99","tid":1745303,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"ac69689ca6ab74660ebcca79c3a25cfa237651a6","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d75df8c9953030b03fcc0624be1d71a1c92d41","tid":1745303,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"搞完後個袋有你指紋屈你謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5277959a1d9fd7d153cab2bed90231551a257a","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f8d75df8c9953030b03fcc0624be1d71a1c92d41","tid":1745303,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"搞完後個袋有你指紋屈你謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"要唔留指紋好多方法姐<br />\n因為有顧慮少少野都唔做<br />\n我代共產黨殺手多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec30b1bdc5d87f393eed7618c0049bc480446b","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:30:28.000Z","msg":"唔好俾香港人死得不明不白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b0ceb851652e31a9d081991807f582ac4b60ea","tid":1745303,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkHeudi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkHeudi.png&h=871c1e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[星期六攻略] 大文宣日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05e0d5012be35c8dc912b2d06eeaff1b507cb923","tid":1745303,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=c93e22e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c3f978a6aa97ff8e6104e35bf03f3c78d13036","tid":1745303,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5277959a1d9fd7d153cab2bed90231551a257a","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f8d75df8c9953030b03fcc0624be1d71a1c92d41","tid":1745303,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"搞完後個袋有你指紋屈你謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"要唔留指紋好多方法姐<br />\n因為有顧慮少少野都唔做<br />\n我代共產黨殺手多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"破壞現場證據呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7091d80b607cdb76af1d3e03981069916f6478ee","tid":1745303,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"唔可以再死得不明不白"},{"pid":"38706e3c88bf6f08a7abda34839dc960c7f933ee","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28c3f978a6aa97ff8e6104e35bf03f3c78d13036","tid":1745303,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5277959a1d9fd7d153cab2bed90231551a257a","tid":1745303,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f8d75df8c9953030b03fcc0624be1d71a1c92d41","tid":1745303,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"搞完後個袋有你指紋屈你謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"要唔留指紋好多方法姐<br />\n因為有顧慮少少野都唔做<br />\n我代共產黨殺手多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"破壞現場證據呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk